chk_billing_concept_rules_range_order.name: chk_billing_concept_rules_range_order
chk_billing_concept_rules_range_order.value: "billing_concept_rules"."value_from" IS NULL OR "billing_concept_rules"."value_to" IS NULL OR "billing_concept_rules"."value_from" <= "billing_concept_rules"."value_to"

chk_billing_cycle_profiles_effective_ord.name: chk_billing_cycle_profiles_effective_order
chk_billing_cycle_profiles_effective_ord.value: "billing_cycle_profiles"."effective_to" IS NULL OR "billing_cycle_profiles"."effective_from" IS NULL OR "billing_cycle_profiles"."effective_from" <= "billing_cycle_profiles"."effective_to"

chk_third_party_names_by_type.name: chk_third_party_names_by_type
chk_third_party_names_by_type.value:
(
        "third_parties"."person_type" = 'NATURAL'
        AND "third_parties"."first_name" IS NOT NULL
        AND "third_parties"."first_last_name" IS NOT NULL
      )
      OR
      (
        "third_parties"."person_type" = 'LEGAL'
        AND "third_parties"."business_name" IS NOT NULL
      )
